            <Abstract ID="Abs1" Language="En">
              <Heading>Abstract</Heading>
              <Para>The restricted flows of a hierarchy of discrete integrable systems are presented. It is shown that integrals of motion and Lax representation for restricted flows as well as a discrete zerocurvature representation for the hierarchy with sources can be deduced from the zero-curvature representation for the hierarchy. Also it is studied how the hierarchy is related to the AKNS hierarchy in the continuous limit.</Para>
            </Abstract>
